<section class="container items-center text-center max-w-[1141px] my-30 bt_sm:mt-[50%]">
    <h2 class="bt_sm:px-[73px] bt_md:px-[201px] px-[246px]">
        Enterprise ERP Solutions for Beverage & Food Industry
    </h2>
    <p class="text-[20px] bt_sm:px-[65px] bt_md:px-[102px] px-[113px] ">
        At Encompass, we’re revolutionizing the beverage and food supply
        chain like no other ERP solution has before. By digitally connecting
        manufacturers, distributors, and retailers, our ERP SaaS solutions
        streamline operations, simplify decision making, and equip businesses
        for success in a fast-changing and unpredictable market.
    </p>

    <div class="pt-[65px] flex bt_sm:block relative">
        <div class="bt_sm:px-[154px]">
            <span class="icomoon icon-solution1 text-[60px]"></span>
            <h3 class="pt-[25px]">Solutions for Manufacturers</h3>
            <p class="pb-[65px] pt-[9px]">
                Over 400 breweries, distilleries, and cideries use Encompass'
                Orchestra Cloud to work from a single source of truth for
                operations, data, and decision making. Streamlining the business
                in this way provides benefits that extend to tier-to-tier automation,
                process transparency, and predictive forecasting.
            </p>
            <a href="#"
                class="no-underline text-[16px] font-bold text-[#e03116] leading-[1.75] tracking-[-0.13px]">EXPLORE
                ORCHESTRA ></a>
        </div>

        <span
            class="icomoon icon-arrows absolute text-[35px] left-[23%] bt_sm:rotate-90 bt_sm:left-0 bt_sm:right-0 bt_sm:top-[31%] bt_sm:text-[30px]"><span
                class="path1"></span><span class="path2"></span><span
                class="path3"></span><span class="path4"></span><span
                class="path5"></span></span>

        <div class="bt_sm:my-[200px] bt_sm:px-[154px] px-[125px]">
            <span class="icomoon icon-solution2 text-[60px]"></span>
            <h3 class="pt-12 px-40">Solutions for Distributors</h3>
            <p class="pb-[65px] pt-[9px]">
                Encompass Cloud powered by the Encompass Platform is specifically
                built for the beverage and food distribution industry. Encompass
                Cloud integrates warehouse management, sales execution, logistics,
                warehouse automation, and retailer ordering tools in a way that makes
                the overall business function smoothly, predictably, efficiently.
            </p>
            <a href="#"
                class="no-underline text-[16px] font-bold text-[#e03116] leading-[1.75] tracking-[-0.13px]">EXPLORE
                EMCOMPASS CLOUD ></a>
        </div>

        <span
            class="icomoon icon-arrows absolute text-[35px] right-[22%] bt_sm:rotate-90 bt_sm:left-0 bt_sm:right-0 bt_sm:bottom-[29%] bt_sm:text-[30px]"><span
                class="path1"></span><span class="path2"></span><span
                class="path3"></span><span class="path4"></span><span
                class="path5"></span></span>

        <div class="bt_sm:px-[154px]">
            <span class="icomoon icon-store text-[60px]"></span>
            <h3 class="pt-[25px] px-[20px]">Solutions for Retailers</h3>
            <p class="pb-[65px] pt-[9px]">
                Our Retail solutions are advancing the way beverage retailers do
                business by optimizing commercial interactions between distributors,
                retailers, and consumers. This is done by consolidating online ordering
                nd retail eCommerce websites with advanced product discovery and delivery
                applications.
            </p>
            <a href="#"
                class="no-underline text-[16px] font-bold text-[#e03116] leading-[1.75] tracking-[-0.13px]">EXPLORE
                EMCOMPASS CLOUD ></a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


